Till The Morning Comes, Hard To Handle, Mama Tried, China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider, Dire Wolf, Cold Rain & Snow, Me & My Uncle, Dark Hollow, Brokedown Palace, Viola Lee Blues-> Cumberland Blues-> Uncle John's Band

Early show Other artist(s): NRPS

reviews.review_text:
100% Killer 5* for the whole Pkg. regardless of any opinion of the playing.  Having both the early and late shows complete with NRPS in this quality is just cool.  

Check out the KPCC/KPFA 12/27-8/70 radio interviews with members of both bands at 4am that circulate to get the back story on the connection between the 2 bands and some other nuggets.
setlist corrections s1t09 is actually called "I'm In Love With You".
i c 5 stars! Love @ 1st sight! 70 most sweet!
enough is never enough Thank you Mr. Charlie for my fifth copy of this show.  It never gets old, only better.  Peace to you.
Thanks for the upgrade I have had a copy of part of this show for aver twenty years. The quality is not bad, but this is no doubt much better. NRPS sound great, too.
great show jerry on pedal steel w/ the New Riders
